<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <%# Email styles need to be inline (client-compatibility constraint) — everything below is
        table markup + inline style attributes, ported structurally from shopmate-backend's own
        app/views/layouts/mailer.html.erb (gray page background, centered 512px white card,
        "Powered by X" footer) — every platform mailer view (account/agency/billing/event/report)
        composes its content from shared/mailer/_heading, _details_table, _button, _notice inside
        this same card, the same "shared chrome, per-mailer content" split shopmate takes.
        ParticipantMailer is the one exception — tenant-branded, fully self-contained,
        `layout false` (see that mailer's own comment) — it never reaches this layout at all. %>
  </head>

  <body style="margin:0;padding:0;background-color:#f2f2f2;">
    <table role="presentation" width="100%" border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" bgcolor="#f2f2f2"
           style="font-family:'Helvetica Neue',Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;padding:8% 0;">
      <tr>
        <td align="center" valign="top">
          <table width="512" style="max-width:512px;width:inherit;">
            <tr>
              <td>
                <table border="0" width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" align="center" style="width:100%;">
                  <tr>
                    <td bgcolor="#ffffff" style="border-radius:8px;padding:45px 50px;">
                      <div style="margin-bottom:12px;">
                        <%= tag.img src: ApplicationHelper::BRAND_LOGO_MAIN_URL, alt: "xEvent", height: 28 %>
                      </div>
                      <%= yield %>
                    </td>
                  </tr>
                </table>

                <table width="100%" border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" align="center">
                  <tr>
                    <td align="center" style="padding:24px 0 0;font-family:'Helvetica Neue',Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;font-size:11px;color:#a6a6b1;">
                      Powered by xEvent
                    </td>
                  </tr>
                </table>
              </td>
            </tr>
          </table>
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table>
  </body>
</html>
